        <img src="https://dummyimage.com/60x60/000/fff&text=Avatar3" alt="Leonel R." width="60" height="60">
        <h4>Leonel R. <span class="role">Designer</span></h4>
        <p>"Top noth support - Flags, programs for, birthday, and occasion welcome are largely still mainstream on paper exceptional capacities."</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <div class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>CUSTOM TEES. ZERO EFFORT. FULL YOU.</h2>
      <p>Just drop your idea, & we'll design it, print it, and ship it.</p>
      <button class="start-now-button">START NOW</button>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-image">
      <img src="https://dummyimage.com/300x200/000/fff&text=CTA+Image" alt="Custom Tees" width="300" height="200">
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

